♪The candid summer♪

177
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:19,700
♪Full of warmth,
you are bathed in sunshine♪

178
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:26,380
♪Along with the boundless blue sky
and white clouds♪

179
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:32,780
♪I am but a lonely cactus♪

180
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:36,100
♪On this sandy shore♪

181
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:39,580
♪Longing for you♪

182
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:42,500
♪To soar like a white dove♪

183
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:50,020
♪If you spread your wings♪

184
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:52,980
♪And wander afar♪

185
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:56,460
♪My shoulders will always♪

186
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:59,460
♪Be here for you♪

187
00:12:02,260 --> 00:12:05,060
♪If your heart holds♪

188
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:10,060
♪Too many longings♪

189
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,060
♪My juice shall♪

190
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:17,940
♪Remember them for you♪
